| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2023-4631 — Recovery Inhibition (noescape)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 9581dfec-d4c7-578e-bb7d-8e7ae5e91cec"
